telijk.\n \nPubliekrechtelijke rechtspersoon is a Public Legal Entity the legal definition is: \nIs the State, a province, a municipality, a water board or a body that has been granted regulatory authority under the Constitution \n\n\nA Privaat rechtelijk organisatin: Private judicial organization: A legal entity under private law is an association, cooperative, mutual insurance company, public limited company, private limited liability company or a foundation.\n\n \n\nSo a publiekrechtelijke rechtspersoon automatically means that you are a Government funded organization. And it is therefore not explained any further on Dutch websites....\n\n\n\nSee also the wikipedia page for universities in The Netherlands:\n\nhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_universities_in_the_Netherlands\n\n \n\nThere are public universities (funded by the Government, like the University of Groningen) and there are private universities (for profit).',2289,'2020-03-24 15:11:11',NULL,NULL,0),(2494,1616,1658,NULL,NULL,2,'AgreementSummary','agreements','This agreement is returned as we await the Partner\'\'s comments on suggested changes and as per email correspondence with Edoardo Zandri 24.3.20. Thank you, Neda',2679,'2020-03-24 15:22:18',NULL,NULL,0),(2495,942,918,0,NULL,2,'AgreementSummary','agreements','Dear Florence, your comment has been addressed. Thank you',2644,'2020-03-24 18:18:28',NULL,NULL,0),(2496,2263,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'DueDiligence','partners','The partner indicated that Global Algorithmic Institute is a fully owned subsidiary of Global AI Co. which is a private partnership and as part of their policy, they do not disclose their financial statements. ',2590,'2020-03-25 09:25:59',NULL,NULL,0),(2497,2143,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'Contactdetails','partners','Dear Paul,\nKindly update HQ address: Shabab Ave, P O Box 835, Manama , Bahrain &  Title of Head of Entity : President .\nthank you',1531,'2020-03-25 09:44:58',NULL,NULL,0),(2498,2143,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'Contactdetails','partners','Conta